name: SuperCells
description: What is the project about? SuperCells is the world's first blockchain-based Stem Cell membership service ecology, creating a metaverse of Stem Cell storage, cultivation, R&D, trading, service and incubation. SuperCells builds a four-in-one metaverse ecology of demand, service, community and supervision, and uses blockchain to economize users' participation behaviors and promote the rapid development of the Stem Cell industry chain to contribute to the cause of human health.
